  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA362-kiḷavi">iḵtuṭaṉpōkāniṉṟa talaimakaṉ ṟalaimakaṭkuc colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">This is what HE who was eloping [with her] said to HER.</p>
        </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA362">
<l>            viṉaiyamai pāvaiyi ṉiyali nuntai</l>
<l>            maṉaivarai yiṟantu vantaṉai yāyiṟ</l>
<l>            ṟalaināṭ ketiriya taṇpata veḻili</l>
<l>            yaṇimiku kāṉat takaṉpuṟam paranta</l>
<l>            kaṭuñcem mūtāy kaṇṭuṅ koṇṭu</l>
<l>            nīviḷai yāṭuka ciṟitē yāṉē</l>
<l>            maḻakaḷi ṟuriñciya parārai vēṅkai</l>
<l>            maṇaliṭu maruṅki ṉirumpuṟam porunti</l>
<l>            yamarvari ṉañcēṉ peyarkkuva</l>
<l>            ṉumarvariṉ maṟaikuvaṉ māa yōḷē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent2">            If you were to come<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">vantaṉai āyiṉ</term> can be either understood as a hypothetical conditional or as a temporal sequence: "once you have come".</note>, traversing the border of your father’s</l>
<l rend="indent2">            house, moving forward like an artfully fashioned doll(?)<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">viṉai amai pāvai</term>: literally (possibly) "a doll effected by work[manship]" - does this under-marked attribute refer to the doll’s being fashioned by an artisan or to something it does?</note>,</l>
<l>        you might play a little,</l>
<l rend="indent">            seeing and taking the quick red cochineals</l>
<l rend="indent2">            spread on the wide back of the forest much decorated</l>
<l rend="indent3">            by properly cool clouds that faced the first day.</l>
<l rend="indent4">            I,</l>
<l rend="indent">            having approached the dark back of the side spread with sand of</l>
<l rend="indent">            the large-trunked Vēṅkai where the young elephant bull has rubbed itself,</l>
<l>        if a fight comes up,</l>
<l rend="indent3">            I am not afraid, I will dispell [them],</l>
<l>        if your people come,</l>
<l rend="indent3">            I will hide myself, o dark one.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
